1.caption_en:
Slide summarizing the three major updates in Release 5.0: End-to-End Coverage (with a growth curve and "Platform Innovation Kit" label), Sustainability (green flower icon), and Introduction — Advanced Tools (a right-hand list of seven tool topics with icons).

